{"type": "article", "id": 4957, "title": "Eatwell 餐具", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-06T07:58:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233516QmlPZNH4rf9F1na5.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t一个托盘、一个碗、一个杯子、一支汤匙以及一把叉子，乍看之下，这套色彩缤纷的餐具除了颜色几无亮点，但仔细研究，却发现处处是玄机。在台湾年轻设计师姚彦慈手中，汤匙与叉子的角度被设计地刚刚好，既易于手握，又比较好舀。杯子内部的高度差设计也使得吸管不易滑动且比较好吸。底部一侧还按照直角进行设计，可以保持重心让食物不会溢出。这是姚彦慈从患有阿兹海默氏症的外婆那里无法自理生活而得到的灵感，因为外婆连要独立进食都很困难，很容易造成食物溢出，于是才有了这套贴心的餐具。目前，Eatwell 已在 Indiegogo 网站上众筹成功，售价 55－110 美元（约合人民币 342－684 元）不等，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/eatwell-tableware-for-people-with-special-needs\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"640\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XODY1Mjk2Mjcy\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n</iframe>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233513IgAQWFjbXk9hrCSV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052335149E8rPbHTh7tJINvR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233514ZMo1erqTzdyiYtDj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233515c7Gh2NlYyxfadX10.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233515Gqlk12mD74zjyZ05.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052335161kwi9JIZNnQe8Kmz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.13125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}